menuconfig BR2_PACKAGE_OPENEMS
	bool "OpenEMS"
	help
	  OpenEMS is an open-source, modular platform designed
	  for energy management. It focuses on monitoring,
	  controlling, and integrating energy storage with
	  renewable energy sources. It also supports various
	  complementary devices and services, such as electric
	  vehicle charging stations, heat pumps, electrolysers,
	  and time-of-use electricity tariffs.
